query:
INSERT INTO app.turbine_layouts(project_id, name, is_primary, added_by, last_updated_by)
             SELECT $1, COALESCE($2, tl.name), COALESCE($3, false), $4, $4
             FROM app.turbine_layouts tl
             WHERE tl.id = $5
               AND tl.project_id = $1
             RETURNING id
